Installation
-----------

Using pip
~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   pip install {{ PKG }}

Using uv (recommended)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   uv pip install {{ PKG }}

For development
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   git clone https://github.com/{{ GITHUB_USERNAME }}/{{ PKG }}.git
   cd {{ PKG }}
   uv sync --all-extras

