Common Tasks
-----------

Running Tests
~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   # Run all tests
   uv run pytest

   # Run with coverage
   uv run pytest --cov

   # Run specific test file
   uv run pytest tests/test_example.py

Code Quality
~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   # Lint code
   uv run ruff check .

   # Format code
   uv run ruff format .

   # Type check
   uv run mypy src

Building Documentation
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: bash

   # Build HTML documentation
   uv run sphinx-build -b html docs docs/_build/html

   # Open in browser
   open docs/_build/html/index.html

