Troubleshooting
--------------

Package not found
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you get an import error, make sure you've installed the package:

.. code-block:: bash

   uv pip list | grep {{ PKG }}

Virtual environment issues
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you're having environment issues, try recreating it:

.. code-block:: bash

   rm -rf .venv
   uv venv
   uv sync --all-extras

